@startuml
title Sequence: Chat with Employer
actor "Job Seeker" as JS
participant "frontend" as UI
participant "Chat Controller" as API
database "Database" as DB
actor "Employer" as EMP

JS -> UI: Open Chat & Type Message
activate UI
JS -> UI: Click Send
UI -> API: Send Message
activate API
API -> DB: Save Message
activate DB
DB --> API: Saved
deactivate DB
API -> EMP: Deliver Message (Socket/Push)
activate EMP
EMP --> API: Acknowledgement
deactivate EMP
API --> UI: Message Sent
deactivate API
deactivate UI
@enduml
